	</Author>	<Contact mailto="isux@qq.com"/>	<Abstract href="http://isux.tencent.com/app/psplay">
		<![CDATA[Ps Play 通过 Wi-Fi，实时在终端设备上预览电脑上 Photoshop 的设计稿，可同步调试及截图保存到移动终端，并可以通过QQ、微信、Email等工具即时分享。是腾讯ISUX 首个独立策划、设计及研发的跨终端应用产品。您可以通过扫描此面板上的二维码，快速连接至 Photoshop。
	
	安装成功后，Ps Play 面板可以在“窗口” > “扩展” 菜单中找到。
	
	--------------------------------------------------------
	
	Ps Play helps to preview the Photoshop action effects on real-time through the Wi-Fi, at the same time you can also take screenshots to record every design process or to share it to friends by QQ, WeChat and Email. Ps Play is the first multi-platform app which was designed and developed by Tencent ISUX independently. 
	
	Once this extension is installed, "Ps Play" can be applied from "Window" menu>"Extension" submenu > "Ps Play".]]>
